===== FoodMod functionality =====
- can only add FoodMods to MenuItemImpls that have fewer than 5 FoodMods.
- can only add FoodMods that have not already been added to an item.
- can only add FoodMods that are not in an item's ingredients.
- there is no pre-specification of what FoodMods can be added to MenuItems,
  it is assumed servers will use AddOns with appropriate MenuItems.